“SHE LOVE”!” ❤️ Fun fact: I wrote the song “She Love” at an open mic event I used to host at @obxbrewingstation This song started out as a total improv where I would shout “SHE LOVE!” and then freestyle verses to follow. At the time, I was also living with my friend @corvinjonnson. It became an on going joke between us where we’d shout “SHE LOVE” to one another from across the house. Later, I moved to San Diego and recorded the song with @e_n_young and had @k_skunkofficial write a verse for it! We then made a music video for the song with @thetevoguy down at sunset cliffs in Ocean Beach! The rest is history. Thanks for singing along with us over the years! Cruise out to one of these upcoming shows and sing it with us even LOUDER then ever as @k_skunkofficial makes his return to the stage!
